title: AWS Chatbot Overview
description:
Learn more about AWS Chatbot at https://amzn.to/33LY03b.
AWS Chatbot is an interactive agent that makes it easy to monitor and interact with your AWS resources in your Slack channels and Amazon Chime chat rooms. With AWS Chatbot you can receive alerts and run commands to return diagnostic information, invoke AWS Lambda functions, and create AWS support cases so that your team can collaborate and respond to events faster.
